strings.Value: "How do I get to Sycamore Hall?"
"How may I help in your war?"
"Forgive me, my Queen, I must go."
[Attack] "It's time to put an end to this alliance."
"All right. I will try to reach the Chief."
"I do not wish to do this."
"It is done. I have defeated Chief Sootscale."
"I will not kill you, Queen. You may take your warriors and leave."
[Finish her] "You will die. That is all that matters."
"Her Magicsty Warrior Queen Bdaah welcome ally her chamber!"
"Just on time, my ally. Shaman Purple Hide pass vicious magic under our nose, and run sacred Sycamore Hall. He have relic-key! Kobold steal our relic, we can follow not. You help us?"
"My guard let you to door. But you need relic. They are two. One have Purple Hide. Where is second, I know not. Think â€” kobold Chief."
"You defeat Chief Sootscale, I reward you generous. Kobold fools all. Without Chief, we win! I want myself cut his silly old head, but he not come fight. Maybe coward. Maybe clever."
"Fine. Then I defeat Chief myself! And wear his hide instead wolf."
"Sweet! I reward and honor you, ally! Now I ready big attack and cut all kobold! Only wait you catch Purple Hide."
"Brave be fight and be not afraid to cut, torture enemy!"
"I disgrace now. We open Sycamore Hall and leave. You worthy warrior. I you remember."
